Linux-Capabilities version 0.01
========================

TODO: Add documentation here :)

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires libcap in order to build and work. In order to build you also need <sys/capability.h>.


